author: app.com
title: Greatest players ever: Here are the dates
text:
MORE In a sense, I'm humbled by the incredible response to my first request for your thoughts on the greatest high school football players ever at the Jersey Shore.
But I'm also not surprised at the outpouring of input I've received over the past two weeks, given the passion exhibited throughout Monmouth and Ocean counties on any given Friday night or Saturday afternoon.
Names have been thrown out there I'd already thought of, others I hadn't considered, and still others I'd never heard of.
But the work isn't done yet.
We've come up with the specific dates for a series of five stories, which will not only recognize many of the finest ever to compete in the area, but trace the rich history of high school football locally.
